OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel due to 'increasing pressures'
OL,6,FA hospital has declared the "highest
OL,7,Flevel of internal escalation" due to
OL,8,F"increasing pressures".
OL,10,FRoyal Lancaster Infirmary announced it
OL,11,Fis at Operational Pressures Escalation
OL,12,FLevel (OPEL) 4, the highest alert
OL,13,Fwithin an NHS hospital.
OL,15,FThe alert is declared when a hospital
OL,16,Fis unable to deliver comprehensive
OL,17,Fcare and patient safety is at risk of
OL,18,Fbeing compromised.
