OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel due to 'increasing pressures'
OL,6,FUniversity Hospitals of Morecambe Bay,
OL,7,Fwhich runs the hospital, has said the
OL,8,Falert will allow them to take
OL,9,F"additional steps to maintain safe
OL,10,Fservices for our patients and help us
OL,11,Fcope with the growing demands".
OL,13,FIn a statement, the Trust added:
OL,14,F"Declaring OPEL 4 enables us to bring
OL,15,Fall our partners in Lancashire and
OL,16,FSouth Cumbria together to focus on one
OL,17,Fthing - the safe and timely care of
OL,18,Fall of our patients.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
