OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel due to 'increasing pressures'
OL,6,F"As always, patient safety must take
OL,7,Fpriority and we need to take action to
OL,8,Fmake sure that those who are more
OL,9,Fclinically urgent get the help they
OL,10,Fneed as quickly as possible."
OL,12,F"Our teams continue to work
OL,13,Fexceptionally hard; and we would like
OL,14,Fto reassure our patients and the
OL,15,Fpublic that in spite of the challenges
OL,16,Ffaced, essential services remain fully
OL,17,Fopen for anyone who needs them so if
OL,18,Fyou require urgent medical help,
OL,19,Fplease continue to come forward."
